---
title: Chickpea Fritter & Feta Lettuce Wraps with Tomato Cucumber Salad & Lemon Yogurt Sauce
description: The best place for these fried chickpea and feta fritters is…nestled into lettuce leaves! (If you answered “in your mouth,” that’s also correct). You’ll sizzle up those savory fritters and load them into baby lettuce leaves along with tomato cucumber salad, tangy yogurt sauce, and chopped parsley for a tantalizing vegetarian meal that pops with fresh flavors.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66c385655cb721784e63699f-6def4927.jpeg
